## Promotion to curated

Maintainers may select community lessons for editorial revision into the
curated tier (separate proprietary repository, see `CONTRIBUTING.md` and
the maind privacy/terms documentation). The original community version
remains under CC BY-SA 4.0 here; the redacted curated version may be
distributed under the proprietary terms of the curated repository.

When a lesson is promoted, the curated version retains an `attribution`
frontmatter block referencing the original community lesson id, original
author, and source repository — preserving Stack-Overflow-style attribution.

